      { "type": "paragraph", "text": "Wiskott-Aldrich syndrome classically presents with recurrent infections, eczema, and thrombocytopenia." }
    ],
    "incorrect": {
      "A": [{ "type": "paragraph", "text": "DiGeorge syndrome causes thymic aplasia with hypocalcemia and conotruncal defects." }],
